title: BBC (UK) Royal Institution Christmas Lectures 2013: Life Fantast
description:
BBC (UK) Royal Institution Christmas Lectures 2013: Life Fantastic

Season 1 Episode 1 of 3

Where Do I Come From? New series. 

In the first of this year's Christmas lectures, Dr Alison Woollard examines how people emerge from a single cell into a multi-trillion-celled organism known as the human body, and using dramatic live experiments she demonstrates each of their functional roles in action

Category Education
